&lt;p&gt;We are seeking candidates based in a major West Coast metro with convenient access to a major airport. Ideal locations include the &lt;strong&gt;San Francisco Bay Area (preferred), Los Angeles/San Diego, or Seattle.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Candidates in the Bay Area are welcome to work from our office on a flexible basis — no set schedule required.&lt;/p&gt;
