&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Identify Opportunities &lt;/strong&gt;–&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;Partner with Growth Team to identify opportunities and generate demand with strategic prospects.&lt;/li&gt;
