&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Develop strong relationships&lt;/strong&gt; – Work with key decision-makers in Talent Acquisition, Engineering, HR, L&amp;amp;D, and technical leadership across prospective customers.&lt;/li&gt;
