&lt;li&gt;Experience writing for developer or HR tech audiences&amp;nbsp; you understand what resonates with people who can smell a generic take from a mile away.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience building or owning a content system, not just contributing to one.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A following or published work that shows you understand what makes content travel.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
