&lt;li&gt;Build and grow your campus’ developer ecosystem&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Inspire classmates to upskill and crack interviews with HackerRank challenges&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the HackerRank team on fun campus initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You’ll fit right in if you:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are a college student (any year, any major)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have a thing for coding, creativity, and community&lt;/li&gt;
