&lt;li&gt;Build the next-gen AI-optimised data layer: clean, structured datasets that power natural language querying and AI add-on features for HackerRank for Work customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own in-product data features - exports, insights dashboards, interview analytics, and the self-serve Custom Reports interface.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enable self-service pipelines for internal teams (AI platform, analytics, go-to-market), reducing ad-hoc data requests and scaling data access across the org.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enforce robust data security - access controls, Apache Ranger policies, and confidence-scoring guardrails for AI-generated outputs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead technical design reviews and define engineering standards for the data team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with PMs and business stakeholders to proactively identify and scope AI-enabled data use cases.&lt;/li&gt;
